                        "In the 2011 Escrows Proposal, the Board proposed to define \u201carea\u201d as \u201ccounty\u201d and to provide that a county would be designated as \u201crural\u201d during a calendar year if:", 
                        "* * * it is not in a metropolitan statistical area or a micropolitan statistical area, as those terms are defined by the U.S. Office of Management and Budget, and either (1) it is not adjacent to any metropolitan or micropolitan area; or (2) it is adjacent to a metropolitan area with fewer than one million residents or adjacent to a micropolitan area, and it contains no town with 2,500 or more residents.", 
